{"tid":1737144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咩今日無呢樣果樣？ 放負撚收皮啦","createTime":"2019-11-19T01:26:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T01:36:30.000Z","uid":41873,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5cc539c13995475b6a5a5b1e740daef14caabb31","tid":1737144,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T01:26:18.000Z","msg":"咩叫<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">長期抗爭</span></span></strong>係咪聽唔撚明<br />\n話俾你地聽 一日達唔成五大訴求<br />\n場抗爭都只會繼續 <br />\n只係模式會唔同左 <br />\n成班話今朝無黎明行動就出黎放負<br />\n我渣車發夢都發到四點幾啦<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你地見唔見到琴晚幾咁團結呀？</span></span></strong><br />\n琴晚有幾撚多新前線呀<br />\n完？邊撚到完？入返你老母個窿度啦"},{"pid":"d8e7cc655490a7612edb6b1c86e2ac7305540676","tid":1737144,"uid":338636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T01:27:37.000Z","msg":"[正能量撚]出去之前，希望你可以睇下呢個po<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1734559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1734559</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>全個連登都係負能量，我要你地有正能量啊</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"7dfb1e7648e8847e250b11a3e55899bd60ae48f7","tid":1737144,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T01:28:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f9b40a04bb94d065d2c74a6cbcd8a50ecfa06fd0","tid":1737144,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T01:28:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a97c3cb9e7a8d31a11d8823612e19c1693eaf0a5","tid":1737144,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T01:28:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c277d59010c93654602f784fa3d6e33c3e47c0a","tid":1737144,"uid":67822,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T01:28:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">切記：不完美 不分化 會改進 不放棄<br />\n<br />\n手足危險我地會去救 係因為我地視每個手足都係家人 即使有生命危險依然會營救手足 因為手足係家人<br />\n<br />\n請認清浪漫主義不現實 武力不及極權政府 道德感召效果不佳 經濟攬炒先係最有效既方法 黃色經濟圈必須擴大<br />\n<br />\n手足唔係個個完美 會犯錯會失誤 但唔係我地放棄既原因 手足少一個都嫌多 AI模型必須改進 唔可以<br />\n一招用到老 見招拆招<br />\n<br />\n任何崗位都有佢既職責 每個行動都會互相影響手足  必須謹慎處理每一條信息 我地冇大台 防人之心不可無 請謹慎判斷消息來源<br />\n<br />\n最後 我愛手足 黑警mon post狗死全家<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hPdXH7c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhPdXH7c.jpg&h=93c034b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"4fb051d1764ea3658827de493853078f1ff2f954","tid":1737144,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T01:28:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5fb42c58436792dc1e13dba41f1ade3b354b28a0","tid":1737144,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T01:29:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c0d2da6d51cbabe66fc0621e0010ec3ec06cf13","tid":1737144,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T01:29:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa3b047762efcaebe694b057bd2760a43e2f2d2d","tid":1737144,"uid":161990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T01:30:01.000Z","msg":"黎明已完撚淨係想朝早唔返工 唔係想幫手抗爭"},{"pid":"cd181cf53d2b9e6a7990c84665297cc4ed00a279","tid":1737144,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T01:30:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b138211f9502acf22f6ec9f6cb4a008e876f9fa4","tid":1737144,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T01:30:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7f4e8e9d1e696d14386a68cf1794ddaa843a2b7a","tid":1737144,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T01:31:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a2abe92ca7162eaf2d18b6480a7fdc7176142ad","tid":1737144,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T01:32:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c32dd103a85585520978082ff65b9e1e59beba9b","tid":1737144,"uid":47309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T01:33:48.000Z","